1. *Pomogla* je sestri da završi zadatak. (She helped her sister to finish the assignment.)
2. Ona je *pomogla* mami da posprema kuću. (She helped her mom to clean the house.)
3. Učenik je *pomogao* učiteljici da razume lekciju. (The student helped the teacher to understand the lesson.)
4. Oni su *pomogli* svom prijatelju da pronađe stan. (They helped their friend to find an apartment.)
5. *Pomoglo* im je da se snađu u novoj situaciji. (It helped them to get used to the new situation.)